#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_protractor.rst:15
msgid ""
"The ruler is an interactive tool where you can drag lines in the scene to "
"measure distances or angles. Optionally snapping to geometry could be activated "
"for better accuracy or to measure wall thickness. The ruler can be accessed "
"from the Tool Shelf."
msgstr ""
"量尺是交互工具，用户可以在屏幕上拖拽直线测量距离或角度。可以激活吸附几何体选项，"
"以获得更精确结果或量测壁厚。从工具栏访问量尺工具。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_protractor.rst:22
msgid "Example of the ruler and protractor."
msgstr "量尺和量角器示例。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_protractor.rst:27
msgid "Example using the ruler to measure thickness."
msgstr "使用量尺来测量厚度的示例。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_protractor.rst:31
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "用法"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_protractor.rst:35
msgid "Here are common steps for using the ruler:"
msgstr "下面是使用量尺的常规操作步骤："

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_protractor.rst:37
msgid "Activate the Ruler from the Tool Shelf."
msgstr "从工具栏激活量尺。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_protractor.rst:38
msgid ""
"Click and drag in the view-port to define the initial start/end point for the "
"ruler."
msgstr "在视窗中单击与拖动，定义量尺的起点/终点。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_protractor.rst:39
msgid ""
"Orbit the view and click on either end of the ruler to re-position it. Holding :"
"kbd:`Ctrl` enables snap to elements."
msgstr ""
"转动视图，单击选择量尺的一端，并重新定位。按住 :kbd:`Ctrl` 启用吸附物体元素(点、"
"线、面)。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_protractor.rst:41
msgid "Click on the middle to measure angles."
msgstr "单击量尺中间部位量测角度。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_protractor.rst:42
msgid ""
"Press :kbd:`Enter` to store the ruler for later use or :kbd:`Esc` to cancel."
msgstr "按 :kbd:`Enter` 保存量尺状态，或者按 :kbd:`Esc` 取消。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_protractor.rst:46
msgid ""
"Editing operations can be used while the ruler is running, however, tools like "
"the knife cannot be used at the same time."
msgstr "量尺工具运行时，可以进行编辑操作。不过一些操作如切割不能同时使用。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_protractor.rst:51
msgid "Unit settings and scale from the scene are used for displaying dimensions."
msgstr "使用场景的单位设置和比例尺显示尺寸。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_protractor.rst:55
msgid "Shortcuts"
msgstr "快捷键"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_protractor.rst:57
msgid ":kbd:`Ctrl-LMB` Adds new ruler."
msgstr ":kbd:`Ctrl-LMB` 添加新量尺。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_protractor.rst:58
msgid ""
":kbd:`LMB` Drag end-points to place them, Hold :kbd:`Ctrl` to snap, Hold :kbd:"
"`Shift` to measure thickness."
msgstr ""
":kbd:`LMB` 拖动端点定位，按住 :kbd:`Ctrl` 吸附，按住 :kbd:`Shift` 测量厚度。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_protractor.rst:59
msgid ""
":kbd:`LMB` Drag center-point to measure angles, drag out of the view to convert "
"back to a ruler."
msgstr ":kbd:`LMB` 拖拽中心点测量角度，拖出视窗回到量尺状态。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_protractor.rst:60
msgid ":kbd:`Delete` Deletes the ruler."
msgstr ":kbd:`Delete` 删除量尺。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_protractor.rst:61
msgid ":kbd:`Ctrl-C` Copies the rulers value to the clipboard."
msgstr ":kbd:`Ctrl-C` 复制尺寸数值到剪贴板。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_protractor.rst:62
msgid ":kbd:`Esc` Exit tool."
msgstr ":kbd:`Esc` 退出。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_protractor.rst:63
msgid ":kbd:`Enter` Saves the rulers for the next time the tool is activated."
msgstr ":kbd:`Enter` 保存量尺状态，下次激活该工具可继续修改。"
